: 2300 lbs Time Since Last Inspection: 28 Hours Engines: 1 Reciprocating Airframe Total Time:  Engine Manufacturer: CONTINENTAL ELT: Installed, not activated Engine Model/Series: IO-360-A Registered Owner: PFEIFER, ROGER A.
Rated Power: 210 hp Operator: PFEIFER, ROGER A.
